WEBVTT

00:05:29.117 --> 00:05:30.768
And he looked at me,

00:05:30.792 --> 00:05:32.165
and he said, "Crazy woman,

00:05:33.157 --> 00:05:37.165
crazy woman, how do you think
I can be a teacher?"

00:05:37.911 --> 00:05:40.395
And I told him,
"I will make you a teacher."

00:05:40.705 --> 00:05:42.848
Finally, he accepted my offer,

00:05:43.554 --> 00:05:46.356
and once I started a class
in his compound,

00:05:46.935 --> 00:05:48.848
the word spread all over.

00:05:49.657 --> 00:05:51.799
In a matter of one year,

00:05:51.823 --> 00:05:54.744
we had 25 schools set up,

00:05:54.768 --> 00:05:57.712
15,000 children going to school,

00:05:57.736 --> 00:05:59.832
and it was amazing.

00:05:59.856 --> 00:06:02.093
(Applause)